                <div class="card bg-dark mb-5">
                    <div class="card-body" style="padding: 4em">
                        <h5 id="abt-title" class="card-title">BuddyVerse</h5>
                        <p id="team-about" class="card-text text-start">Welcome to BuddyVerse, a vibrant and supportive student club dedicated to making your first year of university an unforgettable experience. At BuddyVerse, we understand that transitioning to college life can be both exciting and challenging. That's why we've created a close-knit community that pairs junior students with seasoned senior mentors, providing invaluable guidance and companionship every step of the way.</p>
                        <p id="team-about" class="card-text text-start">But BuddyVerse is more than just academic support – it's a place to forge lasting friendships and create unforgettable memories. We organize a wide range of exciting social events, workshops, and outings that foster connections between first-year students and mentors. From study groups to movie nights, campus tours to game tournaments, you'll find plenty of opportunities to bond with your fellow students and make the most out of your university experience.</p>
                        <p id="team-about" class="card-text text-start">Join us at BuddyVerse and embark on a journey of growth, camaraderie, and self-discovery. Together, we'll navigate the challenges and triumphs of your first year, ensuring that you not only succeed academically but also create cherished memories that will last a lifetime.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
